\begin_layout Section
Design the following finite automata (DFA denotes deterministic and NFA
 - nondeterministic).
 For each one, draw the state diagram, implement it for the FASimulator
 and show its output (copy of the simulator window) for two inputs, one
 ACCEPTED and one REJECTED
\end_layout

